# ============================================
# CONFIGURATION GUIDE
# ============================================
# SHARED VALUES (Same for all members):
#   TELEGRAM_TOKEN: Your Telegram Bot API token for notifications
#   TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID: Your Telegram Chat ID for receiving notifications
#   KITTA: Number of units to apply for (minimum 10)
#   MAX_IPO_PRICE: Maximum IPO price you're willing to pay (won't apply if exceeds this)
#
# INDIVIDUAL VALUES (Different per member in MEMBERS_INFO):
#   name: Identifier for the member (e.g., MEMBER1, MEMBER2)
#   USER_NAME: Member's MeroShare username
#   PASSWORD: Member's MeroShare password
#   DP: Member's Depository Participant with ID in format "DP_NAME (DPID)"
#       Examples: "CITIZENS BANK INTERNATIONAL LIMITED (11700)"
#                 "LAXMI SUNRISE CAPITAL LIMITED (10700)"
#   TRANSACTION_PIN: Member's 4-digit transaction PIN for IPO purchases
#   CRN: Member's CRN (Client Registration Number)
#   BANK_NAME: Member's bank name in UPPERCASE as shown in MeroShare dropdown
#              Examples: "LAXMI BANK LIMITED", "NIC ASIA BANK LIMITED"
#              (if left empty, first option will be selected)
